1207.name: E AlSi 12
1207.Applications: Joining aluminum alloys such as broken gear parts and or other casting parts, also ideal for cladding or rebuilding wornout parts.
1207.Suitable_For: cast aluminium with more than 7% silicium, 3.2581, 3.2583, 3.2381, 3.2383, 3.2373, G-AlSi 12, G-AlSi 12 (Cu), G-AlSi 10 Mg, G-AlSi 10 Mg (Cu), G-AlSi 9 Mg,
